<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5771741>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1–2. Morphology of Lista spp. 1. Head of L. strumiformis sp. nov.; 2. Venation of L. ficki. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5771741/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5771743>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3–5. Morphology of Lista spp. 3. Adult of L. strumiformis sp. nov.; 4. Male genitalia of L. haraldusalis; 5. Female genitalia of L. haraldusalis. Scale bar: Fig. 3=2.0 mm; Figs 4, 5=0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5771743/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5771749>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–27. Male genitalia of Lista spp. 22. L. angustusa, slide No. RH16132; 23. L. ficki, slide No. RH16122; 24. L. furcellata sp. nov., paratype, slide No. RH16369; 25. L. furciillatusa, slide No. RH16171; 26. L. gilvasa, slide No. RH16120; 27. L. insulsalis, slide No. RH15145. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5771749/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5771753>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28–33. Male genitalia of Lista spp. 28. L. longifundamena, slide No. RH15155; 29. L. menghaiensis, slide No. RH16155; 30. L. menglaensis, slide No. RH16397; 31. L. monticola, slide No. WYP05169; 32. L. serrata sp. nov., holotype, slide No. RH16380; 33. L. sichuanensis, slide No. RH16133. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5771753/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5771755>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34–37. Male genitalia of Lista spp. 34. L. strumiformis sp. nov., paratype, slide No. RH15161; 35. L. zhengi sp. nov., paratype, slide No. RH16362; 36. L. variegata, slide No. RH15157; 37. L. yunnanensis sp. nov., holotype, slide No. RH15273. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5771755/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

